{"tid":525784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖] 深圳寶安國際機場「無限六角窗」讓人頭皮麻","createTime":"2018-01-11T04:25:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T10:41:28.000Z","uid":35468,"like":24,"dislike":165,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"cb2e2fcf8c73f8a5f59b2bf769d663d112611b67","tid":525784,"uid":35468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/02/realtime/4389371.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Frealtime%2F4389371.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=00403f46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/02/realtime/4389372.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Frealtime%2F4389372.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=46920a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/02/realtime/4389373.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Frealtime%2F4389373.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=7b23e6fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/02/realtime/4389374.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Frealtime%2F4389374.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=cb3660ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/01/02/realtime/4389375.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F01%2F02%2Frealtime%2F4389375.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=f6878c36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n慎入！密集恐懼地獄 機場「無限六角窗」讓人頭皮麻<br />\n<br />\n位於深圳的寶安國際機場，每年旅客吞吐量可達4,000萬人次，是大陸重要的國際機場。寶安機場的特色之一，就是運用大量的六角、圓形洞口作為裝飾，因此也被許多網友暱稱「密集恐懼症的地獄」，還有人表示「一看就頭皮發麻」。<br />\n<br />\n寶安機場名列世界百大機場之一，同時也是深圳、中國南方等航空公司的樞紐基地，亦是許多旅客進出深圳的重要門戶。對於旅客而言，寶安機場最大的特色，就是強烈的建築風格，所帶來密集恐懼的壓力。密集物恐懼症（Trypophobia）意思是指對於排列密集的小物、孔洞十分敏感，包括青蛙卵、蜂巢、蓮蓬等物，往往都會令密集恐懼症患者感到不適。<br />\n<br />\n寶安機場的機場航站大樓內，就是因為天花板使用了無數的窗口作為裝飾或採光功能，讓排列密集又不斷重複出現的六角型、方型、圓形充斥整座機場，還會依照地點位置的不同，而有不同的排列差異，連空調出風口，都製作成巨大的蓮蓬頭。因此儘管已啟用多年，但寶安機場的風格，仍然常會引起熱議。小胖林育群就曾於臉書打卡，表示「這個機場是.......要逼死有密集恐懼症的人嗎？絕對不能抬頭」<br />\n<br />\n儘管裝潢令部分旅客不適，但是透過寶安機場，旅客可延伸至錦繡中華、民俗文化村、世界之窗、野生動物園等觀光旅遊景點，仍然是重要的旅遊環節之一。"},{"pid":"120daad735074abfc1bd7600bc21124446ea8646","tid":525784,"uid":4811,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:29:17.000Z","msg":"嘩屌！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93011f7a65f619a38194ef539e32134beaf54c7f","tid":525784,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T04:32:09.000Z","msg":"去過幾次...真係唔敢望上去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19fe7b3b968f865706181f1e90425b5a884a975e","tid":525784,"uid":62409,"like":121,"d